metadata.description:
a poor car turned viral.
a car that had a hard night with friends.
a car born poor. 
a car with a dream which never became reality.
a car for the community.
a car for me, for you and for each of us.
a car with a clear statement to the big guys out there.
i'm coming to get you and I'll get you.
